{"tid":146134,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[足球魚腩國] 去聖馬力諾參觀主場 (錄播半live)","createTime":"2017-03-06T22:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T15:10:58.000Z","uid":61332,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d3c8b567bbbfadd11f8c884d4084251d3927dbc","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-06T22:45:18.000Z","msg":"第一次連登開post, 唔鐘意嘅唔好屌太大力<br />\n<br />\n半live嘅原因係電話卡收得好差，依家都係坐喺hostel先有stable network<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且都係用意粉嘅電話網<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見好似都唔算多人去呢個地方，就隨便寫吓介紹吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實今次嘅旅程唔係專登去聖馬力諾，不過有睇波嘅人都知聖馬力諾貴為國際魚腩（FIFA ranking包尾左唔知幾多年），場場都俾人大炒，入到波已經全國放假，唔知廚師定文員仔打緊國家隊正選，真係隨時喺街行過一個後生仔都有可能係國家隊成員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吓吓話人魚腩都唔太好，因為人地梯隊其實唔失禮，對於一個只有~33,000人口嘅國家嚟講，算係咁<br />\n<br />\n我今次就因為想睇祖雲達斯，又辭左工冇耐，決定起行去意大利一個月搵保方揸佢jerjer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為保方年屆39，再唔去真係唔會睇到佢現場，所以窮都要去，破產都要睇佢歐聯，否則終身抱憾<br />\n<br />\n相信好多人都唔知聖馬力諾喺邊，甚至聽都未聽過<br />\n有聽過嘅可能係有睇賽車F1？又或者有睇開波而認識？又或者你本身好鐘意毒在房中瘋狂睇世界地圖？<br />\n<br />\n點都好啦，簡介少少<br />\n呢個國家係全球第五細嘅小國，第一個係梵帝崗，其他三個不在討論之列，第五就係聖馬力諾<br />\n山城一個，由公元301年已經獨立左出嚟，係民主共和國之中歷史最悠久嘅一個，國家總面積61.2平方公里<br />\n<br />\n可能你會問我：吓？咁即係幾多個香港呀？<br />\n我會答你：0.055個左右啦，屌咁講完你都唔知幾大架啦，嗱，港島就80.4平方公里，咁San Marino咪3/4個港島多少少囉，即係北角畫條線落赤柱，北角以東嘅唔要，大概就係San Marino咁大啦<br />\n(呢啲資料都可以wiki搵到，喺seed同丁圖都係求合集，懶人包當道嘅年代又點會搵丫)<br />\n<br />\nSan Marino國旗<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/B65AOje.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FB65AOje.jpg&h=31d43f77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上帝視角<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Wzz2GnD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWzz2GnD.jpg&h=aa222a65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://www.sanmarino.sm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sanmarino.sm&d=xhW6TUFsNmSNLx%2F%2BVUQDb9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=7639bbfe\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sanmarino.sm</a><br />\n<br />\n每次同人講到去意大利包含住嘅兩個小國，啲人就問我：吓？唔係得一個咋咩？唔係得Vatican City<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後俾個咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘅樣我<br />\n<br />\n咁我唯有show張google map俾佢睇啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/oCHqCH9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FoCHqCH9.jpg&h=caac9f47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢所處位置其實係喺意大利中部，不過不論Firenze, Roma都冇車直接上去，可能中間太多山？唔知點解啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我今朝出發嘅位置係係Firenze，我會揀搭火車去Bologna狹去Rimini，然後轉巴士上山<br />\n因為Rimini同San Marino本身都唔係咩大區，所以flixbus都冇站，乖乖地火車轉巴士上去實際<br />\n要平又好彩嘅話Firenze上去San Marino大概4.5小時 (搭regional嘅慢車班次)，我就因為唔知係咪check班次check錯左，要俾貴十歐多少少，搭左快車去Bologna<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n沖個涼再繼續，手機打得好慢，點解我唔帶notebook呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望有人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd2e9978c53251b7c41f31f42409b9b9b258eb9c","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:01:58.000Z","msg":"咁我出發點就firenze，大家出發點唔同嘅就可能其他意粉車站，隔離床位就話直接飛Bologna去Rimini轉車上，不過人地倫敦巨撚，有ryanair幫手，亞洲過去賤過地底泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFirenze Santa Maria Novella車站，有去過Firenze過去邪塔同cinque terre嘅巴絲應該唔會陌生<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/SMJX7FC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSMJX7FC.jpg&h=aa731a8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n買飛，直接去other打Rimini<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/B8jSoBo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FB8jSoBo.jpg&h=94f3b413&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱check過原來有啲飛&euro;13.8有交易<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係會趕唔切尾班巴士上San Marino，真係唔會買到咁貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/H907n2q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FH907n2q.jpg&h=db436b28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已經欲哭無淚<br />\n所以巴絲打記得記得check清楚火車班次<br />\n<br />\n同埋意國火車記得上車前要去吸印拮窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/gQDFIZu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FgQDFIZu.jpg&h=c2d3ac62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搵呢部綠色機隨便隊入去就得，唔拮啲意大利月台姐姐會唔俾你入閘，所以要預留時間"},{"pid":"89a4f7a367ba2005ceb4ac51f821179a467caa72","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:03:55.000Z","msg":"補返張死圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/SMJX7FZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FSMJX7FZ.jpg&h=c987308b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c19e7e139adc2f3aac82ff52f95fe278e5ffa70d","tid":146134,"uid":13327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:07:49.000Z","msg":"正   留名跟進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3a13d04b392ab091f96543b9d190ff3e87ac4b","tid":146134,"uid":4316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:08:22.000Z","msg":"正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打係自己一條友去？ 淨係去意大利同聖馬力諾？"},{"pid":"458ea5e0feab106da6fff0542c748c4b8d79ff6f","tid":146134,"uid":85946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22eec3c27abe8e024446e6ddc0d3f575ed646fef","tid":146134,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:11:59.000Z","msg":"高質貼留名<br />\n<br />\n上次去意大利打算去埋 San Marino<br />\n不過條路好轉折, 最後無去"},{"pid":"e74b11a6d007d8251274d9487e112ff5d551607e","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:12:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打係自己一條友去？ 淨係去意大利同聖馬力諾？</blockquote><br />\n9成半時間自己一個，hostel識到人啱嘴形就一齊行<br />\n比利時第一站，落左盧森堡一轉，然後去都靈兜左個圈，攞左兩位球星簽名<br />\n之後就去馬爾他，再去西西里島，慢慢南到北行意大利，San Marino係插曲，最尾米蘭返布魯塞爾逛多幾日走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e29ce245bf2911bc1e16394e793f7ea44fb44a00","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:15:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高質貼留名<br />\n<br />\n上次去意大利打算去埋 San Marino<br />\n不過條路好轉折, 最後無去</blockquote><br />\n值得去架，唔去蝕哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日個天清到望到克羅地亞對開海岸，手機影出嚟唔係好清就是了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb80379574ca8dac12d2d8a2e101bd4cbddb71ba","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:29:16.000Z","msg":"見有人睇，盡力更新吓<br />\n對返張飛，睇返班次去月台<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/rJkgQLp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrJkgQLp.jpg&h=fdf80707&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上車 隔離有鬼妹<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Rdmjmyx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRdmjmyx.jpg&h=98212ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇鬼妹圖唔好屌我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到Bologna<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fo59pCJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffo59pCJ.jpg&h=b81edb2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺意大利搭火車搭regional我有個習慣，就係會去bigletteria啲機度撳多次出發點同目的地，為左睇清楚班regional嘅編號，出發時間同所需時間，先再睇水牌去月台，睇duration嘅原因係上車基本上都唔多知去到邊，車上面多數都收唔到data，以防萬一，較定鬧鐘，較早五分鐘，醒返就執野落車啱啱好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HVF6F4x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHVF6F4x.jpg&h=c8e6be12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d1f3297d92cd4504b38f31d338e859b405f1164","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:33:29.000Z","msg":"又手殘打錯code死圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBologna<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fo59pCJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffo59pCJ.jpg&h=b81edb2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n順帶一提，呢個站月台13-18喺地底，唔記得係咪13開始，但1-11就喺地面，都唔係咁快好似地鐵咁過對面就轉到車<br />\n我就跑左分幾鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1fed929c67911a38fb999998e85799f88d6591a","tid":146134,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:37:39.000Z","msg":"咁細地方都有個足球場<br />\n又冇高樓<br />\n<br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"031c20fa16ddacd9a7096ae0c08438f136e6ddb9","tid":146134,"uid":26219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:40:55.000Z","msg":"LM 繼續睇"},{"pid":"93bedc664f7df5db90c557077fa0d171e356ba54","tid":146134,"uid":87577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:43:40.000Z","msg":"HQ po lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62eb9876b526065e07ad098d2a9929f44c216b61","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:54:00.000Z","msg":"打埋呢篇訓啦，聽日仲要行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n路上風景<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/W2uXR8w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FW2uXR8w.jpg&h=46ce1fa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地意粉啲運油車靚幾多，雖然入面唔知係咪油<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/VHiMSni.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVHiMSni.jpg&h=0a625c5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天色唔錯，還可以，雖然夜晚落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5NAHQFE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5NAHQFE.jpg&h=a654afaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抵達Rimini<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/j8EJNkM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fj8EJNkM.jpg&h=e04e5507&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出左站之後，前面有個bus ticket office，唔洗理佢，過對面馬路右轉，街角有間餐廳，隔離就係Burger King<br />\n再喺呢排巴七站行到尾就係上San Marino嘅站<br />\n飛上車買，盛惠&euro;5<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/WL9PpSd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWL9PpSd.jpg&h=eedc8efc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fZUTQNI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FfZUTQNI.jpg&h=ce05ba7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jB6rtMv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjB6rtMv.jpg&h=f705100b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/KS9RQdI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKS9RQdI.jpg&h=e13c5be1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁由於歐洲痾篤尿係非常之貴嘅關係，我強烈建議大家經過左3個鐘火車爆膀胱之旅後入一入Burger King痾個jer<br />\n因為係<span style=\"color: red;\">免費</span>架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n訓先，趁隔離有個大叔冇打鼻鼾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明天繼續，一有時間同網絡就更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67076fd0d3d4328472daf6d282dfc279d222f025","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T00:58:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁細地方都有個足球場<br />\n又冇高樓<br />\n<br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地個主場坐得七千人，比起大球場嚟講真係細一截，不過球迷反應方面啦喎.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba865b773780ff73c31457864724fcf911e21d68","tid":146134,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T01:05:57.000Z","msg":"意粉留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次回覆就決定留喺呢個高汁Post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54d3f8712546d3f102e5544ba8257c2fc30fb8df","tid":146134,"uid":7699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T01:12:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁細地方都有個足球場<br />\n又冇高樓<br />\n<br />\n香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地個主場坐得七千人，比起大球場嚟講真係細一截，不過球迷反應方面啦喎.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大球場大有咩用 一年有幾可坐得滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係得7人欖球或者英超隊黎踢先滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBetween 留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447eb2381b29e1f2aac1932293da30e57b847e58","tid":146134,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T01:15:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7a05adb0eaf5b65418d83fa7867df0596f0cb4c5","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:27:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>意粉留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第一次回覆就決定留喺呢個高汁Post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我應該會去參觀聖西路，雖然我唔係米蘭fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a78d6a5b7f5ba9837c7eba67db98f9377fb251","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:30:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>意粉火車飛真係成日唔同價，好狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講起呢樣我就嬲啦<br />\n因為下一站係威尼斯<br />\n全部平車飛都喺朝早7點半前開哂車<br />\n但係咁早根本冇巴士落到去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我喺度諗，不如今晚夜媽媽行路落去</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲可以夜遊人地個主場<br />\n不過要2點出發夜行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3eadf1e78d2d9d2ce118170c8da80cf3fb8ec94","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T10:36:46.000Z","msg":"出發行山，返嚟單機update<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79802704345d03f9e151b2c4423f2cf38518e35c","tid":146134,"uid":61229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:32:56.000Z","msg":"support<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f5b9dbc99a592782b0e717552ac314b963ac5d0","tid":146134,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T12:57:26.000Z","msg":"留明"},{"pid":"57b45cd3f473f12212dc73d24d5d997e00a7edd9","tid":146134,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T13:12:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f7bb1788c17279dff4a9cc4682fabf474f6cdc24","tid":146134,"uid":14459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"前一兩年係Rimini exchange表示睇到巴打個post好撚親切<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你形容出rimini車站之後過對面馬路burger king我仲記得好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSan Marino我都有上過兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a827890fc3d71660407be3426ce7c922a34dcec","tid":146134,"uid":33424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:17:29.000Z","msg":"樓主係都靈睇祖記training?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋而家意大利治安比以前有冇改善到?"},{"pid":"f063d2cc419307db748e602693eb356dcc46a838","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T23:45:15.000Z","msg":"多謝有睇post嘅巴打，趡未訓着update吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e32a3154ccc36c682e7aa0150589db75ed96dfe9","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T23:46:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>意粉火車飛真係成日唔同價，好狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講起呢樣我就嬲啦<br />\n因為下一站係威尼斯<br />\n全部平車飛都喺朝早7點半前開哂車<br />\n但係咁早根本冇巴士落到去<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我喺度諗，不如今晚夜媽媽行路落去</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲可以夜遊人地個主場<br />\n不過要2點出發夜行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可以上網買定先，之後唔知點樣去拎飛<br />\n上網買多數有優惠，但買即日都係貴，要早買先平</blockquote><br />\n有時睇吓啲goeuro都會有意想不到嘅驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最衰冇船搭去Venezia<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我聽日離開San Marino 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c66ad0d4f7d6ffef15b2d3edcf338976bb02e789","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T23:48:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前一兩年係Rimini exchange表示睇到巴打個post好撚親切<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你形容出rimini車站之後過對面馬路burger king我仲記得好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSan Marino我都有上過兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打咁犀利去到Rimini exchange<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔打算停Rimini呀<br />\n行程開始趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"914274c2382ca805c104d156868c3c642fe07ce5","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T23:52:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係都靈睇祖記training?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋而家意大利治安比以前有冇改善到?</blockquote><br />\n屌你又知嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入左去拎左邦路斯同巴沙利簽名 <br />\n嚟緊14號去睇波圖(如無意外)<br />\n<br />\n真係相認就電話相認啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n知得都應該有我電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n意大利治安唔算差<br />\n係Napoli同Catania比較差，就算係位處西西里島嘅Palermo我都覺得ok<br />\n同埋幾時都小心財物，尤其遊客區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14fa4eacbab44cf58fabf4b3d11a860bebb257b7","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T23:59:03.000Z","msg":"同埋我決定唔夜媽媽走，Hostel個負責人太好人，唔忍心兩點嘈醒佢老人家check out<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寧願俾貴少少火車算<br />\n得佢一個人打點，好辛苦<br />\n遲吓我會介紹埋呢間hostel，應該一個人嚟計，住呢度算最平，呢邊都係酒店多，hostel唔覺眼有"},{"pid":"d7655fbc6201ce9bb8c0ba1d80fe5a8ca8b7a590","tid":146134,"uid":72702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T00:04:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打係自己一條友去？ 淨係去意大利同聖馬力諾？</blockquote><br />\n9成半時間自己一個，hostel識到人啱嘴形就一齊行<br />\n比利時第一站，落左盧森堡一轉，然後去都靈兜左個圈，攞左兩位球星簽名<br />\n之後就去馬爾他，再去西西里島，慢慢南到北行意大利，San Marino係插曲，最尾米蘭返布魯塞爾逛多幾日走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊兩個球星？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n保方馬少？<br />\nAzzurri 加Rossoneri撚留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd7d95932c0b643ac6db1147fae8ebe95a62be9b","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T00:05:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n巴打係自己一條友去？ 淨係去意大利同聖馬力諾？</blockquote><br />\n9成半時間自己一個，hostel識到人啱嘴形就一齊行<br />\n比利時第一站，落左盧森堡一轉，然後去都靈兜左個圈，攞左兩位球星簽名<br />\n之後就去馬爾他，再去西西里島，慢慢南到北行意大利，San Marino係插曲，最尾米蘭返布魯塞爾逛多幾日走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊兩個球星？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n保方馬少？<br />\nAzzurri 加Rossoneri撚留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邦路斯巴沙利，期待嘅保方攞唔到，下星期返都靈再試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da093fb8d217c4cc5dc75a946992ee4d4df0f128","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T00:24:46.000Z","msg":"抵步一落車，屌！好撚正呀個view<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/VA6wTAA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FVA6wTAA.jpg&h=9cdaafbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/a8Os3U6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fa8Os3U6.jpg&h=02186bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢地啲車牌，由於San Marino並唔係歐盟國家，所以格式上冇好似其他國家嘅車有個字頭，例如意粉有I，比利時有BL咁<br />\n取而代之係國徽一個，英文字一個加四位數字<br />\n因為國家人口唔多，咁嘅格式已經夠發牌俾240,000部車 (我冇計I同O)<br />\n其實個車牌都幾靚，用返白同淺藍做主色<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/K7ZiuUp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FK7ZiuUp.jpg&h=9e8fa6e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於我唔記得down定offline map，所以我根本連自己落完車喺邊個位都唔知，又收唔到電話，所以上嚟記得down定map<br />\n如果唔係就好似我呢條鳩頭咁盪失路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/cx82BEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fcx82BEQ.jpg&h=768a959b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又唔洗太驚嘅，影吓相先，難得嚟到山城，反正船到橋頭自然直，最柒咪飛的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/92cmXQg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F92cmXQg.jpg&h=20c9fc56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行行吓見到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/HX4snhU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHX4snhU.jpg&h=f7f19ea5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b97f2de2a47637ca61c679751dd59bdaf3d5523","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:12:29.000Z","msg":"San Marino嘅旅程完畢，我會慢慢補返呢三日兩夜嘅趣事，唔會寫遊記都爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啱啱參觀完San Marino嘅主場<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b7e2bfc7692a81c103c9e97cc0da1e35b362199","tid":146134,"uid":33787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:24:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2f6bfd241bda3a10854a742403ef058dac4837a","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:46:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無去比錢貼張郵票上passport</blockquote><br />\n屌唔記得左<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22d17dda90284ed9dee63345d7d17d3aa989faf8","tid":146134,"uid":27991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T14:52:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>San Marino嘅旅程完畢，我會慢慢補返呢三日兩夜嘅趣事，唔會寫遊記都爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啱啱參觀完San Marino嘅主場<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n留名參考下次去"},{"pid":"fb464178240f5556114f8f2de6e617cc0ee3a88d","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:00:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>San Marino嘅旅程完畢，我會慢慢補返呢三日兩夜嘅趣事，唔會寫遊記都爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啱啱參觀完San Marino嘅主場<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n留名參考下次去</blockquote><br />\n其實有得自己租車會方便啲，我今次係好彩，如果唔係淨靠行都幾係野，差不多完我會交代吓<br />\n今日感覺勁warm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9cb68e7111e7674291698409a05546cb5d8ed1","tid":146134,"uid":62296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:08:45.000Z","msg":"都係因為足球先識聖馬力諾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留名支持"},{"pid":"6ca0a2cbaca651bf8229c5a15997fd2b50cdd83c","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:19:23.000Z","msg":"行到度閘，發現救星，即刻影低<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/v3QDd7n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fv3QDd7n.jpg&h=ad48feae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過地圖唔夠detail，只能靠佢知道自己位置，點樣落去左上角另一個市區仍然唔知，我hostel喺嗰一帶，呢個我有mark低<br />\n<br />\n去到度閘，望吓右邊，有個奇怪山窿，再右少少，原來有路上centro<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/dwvpptV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdwvpptV.jpg&h=3cc8a123&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/7dWyWq5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7dWyWq5.jpg&h=2fc4d6dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個山窿就係咁細，入面冇想睇我仆街嘅香港人所期待嘅ii，反而有張凳，有本簿，眼力好少少會見到本簿喺門口<br />\n下次有連登仔去可以搵吓我墨寶<br />\n<br />\nbtw，我其實對呢度呢認識唔深，無謂喺度班門弄斧，對呢啲古蹟教堂並唔會作詳細簡介，亦都冇去哂咁多個point<br />\n留返各位睇完下次去嘅時候親身認識<br />\n<br />\n依家準備搭車去Venezia"},{"pid":"f7ed50c431e41f034cbabbf85be8e1f8978cfa55","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:20:51.000Z","msg":"sorry又要補圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/7dWyWQ5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F7dWyWQ5.jpg&h=ad35547e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fdc33d0021d5a756b1dd4bdf0704c529e76d1437","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:21:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係因為足球先識聖馬力諾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留名支持</blockquote><br />\nsame here<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係有去佢地圖家主場架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b796bba1c357b732273fa7cb9a44f564d7214ad","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T15:33:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>都係因為足球先識聖馬力諾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留名支持</blockquote><br />\nsame here<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係有去佢地圖家主場架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0ebf1080befd3dcd38ec3a575341005d61d9d5","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T16:06:13.000Z","msg":"轉上山窿右邊個入口，向上行就入市內<br />\ncentro地區係有城牆圍住，好易認<br />\n嚟到呢間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/Fa81V6l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FFa81V6l.jpg&h=6c9ed133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇心情深究，繼續上，向唔知存唔存在嘅山路捷徑或纜車進發<br />\n<br />\n過左個唔記得乜名嘅piazza，左轉入去就差唔多到纜車站，到站前有呢幅大畫，似係一個古代outdoor theatre嘅東西<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/3DS4PwJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F3DS4PwJ.jpg&h=7f7a9c6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊緣位置，應該向西北<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/lrhg8dj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Flrhg8dj.jpg&h=8395a0bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小背光，手機質素有限，見諒<br />\n<br />\n呢邊應該向東北<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/fz10UcQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffz10UcQ.jpg&h=6329ac55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔難發現一樣野：纜車纜，但纜車呢？<br />\n屌原來冇開<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲係數以月計，山路又搵唔到，唔通碌落去咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁我心諗橫掂都上左嚟，行吓先返落去，反正都係要兜<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/b8hBDdA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fb8hBDdA.jpg&h=707e3a35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n結果俾我兜左去自由廣場同政府總部<br />\n冇錯，後面嗰係的確係政總，人口先得3萬3，政府咪又係嗰二三十個，細細幢幾滴骰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果政總俾人包圍應該除左游繩之外走唔甩，終於明點解古代皇帝被攻陷除左自殺別無他法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政總好似有參觀時間，唔知我有冇記錯<br />\n鳩up時間：人地係自由民主社會，而且半年大選一次，係唔係一人一票我就冇問，不過半年一次我冇聽錯的話就千真萬確<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1c9987e98660285391ac6081e3f482a3acf840","tid":146134,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T17:27:31.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔記得問巴打有冇機會幫手買聖馬利諾國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01a147fd795aec8c0c03168c0ceb049536eb39bf","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T18:16:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔記得問巴打有冇機會幫手買聖馬利諾國旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇啦，我走左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都好唔捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係繼花蓮之後我第二個好唔捨得走嘅地方<br />\n走嗰時眼濕濕同hostel個負責人道別<br />\n順帶一提，佢係米蘭fans，唔鐘意祖記<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62561b488ea9a76a88c2935a13934643e36b336","tid":146134,"uid":61332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T23:24:34.000Z","msg":"psg咁都搞唔掂巴塞冇心情update<br />\n明天訓醒再up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb8ffa4994094330245017633f86414eb0bade9","